<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2024-09-03T03:00:00-04:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2024-09-03T03:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-03T03:00:00-04:00</updated><title>沃尔沃EX90首驾：未完全出炉</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;沃尔沃 EX90&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/N5lmP3YY7h0FQQCbW6K3_4NDpr4=/0x176:4080x2896/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image /73560222/PXL_20240821_175355660.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;沃尔沃 EX90 推迟了一年，但仍然无法兑现其承诺的所有功能。 &lt;/em>; |图片：Abigail Bassett&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;沃尔沃的新款旗舰电动汽车拥有大量豪华花哨的功能，但其部分技术仍待确定。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https: //www.theverge.com/2024/9/3/24233412/volvo-ex90-hands-on-specs-range-tech-lidar&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/3/24233412/volvo-ex90-hands-on-specs-range-tech-lidar" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/3/24233412/volvo-ex90-hands-on-specs-range-tech-lidar</id><author><name>阿比盖尔·巴塞特</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-02T17:06:43-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-02T17:06:43-04:00</updated><title>巴西最高法院小组维持 X 禁令，但 Starlink 拒绝遵守</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;X 徽标的矢量拼贴画。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/hcpnXcYyjr1zJfkGnEWyUJpHDI8=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73559648/STK160_X_TWITTER_2__C.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;shd178&quot;>;由五名巴西最高法院法官组成的小组&lt;a href=&quot;https://noticias.stf.jus.br/postsnoticias/ stf-confirma-decisao-que-suspendeu-ox-antigo-twitter-em-todo-o-pais/&quot;>;周一投票维持决定&lt;/a>; (&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.documentcloud. org/documents/25084886-voto-alexandre-de-moraes-suspensao-x-stf-plenario-virtual-1?responsive=1&amp;amp;title=1&quot;>;PDF&lt;/a>;）要求国家电信局 (Anatel)限制对 X 的访问，该服务以前称为 Twitter。法官亚历山大·德·莫赖斯&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/30/24231286/x-brazil-ban-elon-musk-legal-representative&quot;>;于周五发布了该禁令&lt;/a >; 回应 X 所有者埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 拒绝遵守法院命令封锁某些账户并指定在该国的法定代表人。其他四位法官现已支持这一决定。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;cMzHxg&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.poder360.com.br/poder-justica/1a-turma-do-stf- forma-maioria-para-manter-suspensao-do-x/&quot;>;&lt;em>;Poder360&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://oglobo.globo.com/politica/noticia/​​2024/ 09/02/suspensao-do-x-os-cinco-recados-da-primeira-turma-no-julgamento-que-confirmou-decisao-de-moraes.ghtml&quot;>;&lt;em>;环球&lt;/em>;&lt;/ a>; 报道称，三位法官克里斯蒂亚诺·扎宁 (Cristiano Zanin)、弗拉维奥·迪诺 (Flávio Dino) 和卡门·卢西亚 (Cármen Lúcia) 完全支持德·莫赖斯 (de Moraes) 的裁决，而第四位法官路易斯·福克斯 (Luiz Fux) 对对通过 VPN 规避禁令的人处以罚款持保留态度，他说只有那些发布犯罪信息...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/2/24234349/x-twitter-ban-brazil-supreme-court-elon-麝香-莫拉斯&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/2/24234349/x-twitter-ban-brazil-supreme-court-elon-musk-moraes" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/2/24234349/x-twitter-ban-brazil-supreme-court-elon-musk-moraes</id><author><name>理查德·劳勒</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-02T15:38:16-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-02T15:38:16-04:00</updated><title>据 Politico 报道，雅各布·沃尔正在以化名经营一家人工智能游说公司</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;放射性背景下杰克·伯克曼和雅各布·沃尔的图像&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/o02Xh_impifMoU5r2lMq_PxKE78=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox -cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73559457/acastro_illo_226067_0002.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;亚历克斯·卡斯特罗/The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;vjXoIf&quot;>;雅各布·沃尔和杰克·伯克曼是&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2022/7/22/23273280/jacob-wohl-jack-burkman-predator-dc-film-shoot-assault-allegations- payment&quot;>;极右派活动人士&lt;/a>;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.npr.org/2022/12/01/1140096697/jacob-wohl-jack-burkman-robocalls-ohio-sentence&quot;>;被定罪的重罪犯&lt;/a>;以及&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.cnn.com/2018/10/31/media/gateway-pundit-robert-mueller-false-allegations/index.html&quot;>;可疑的政治噱头的工程师&lt;/a >;。 &lt;em>;Politico&lt;/em>;报道&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.politico.com/news/2024/09/02/jacob-wohl-jack-burkman-ai-lobbying-pseudonyms-00176917&quot;>;他们现在还运营着 LobbyMatic&lt;/a>;，这是一家销售“&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.lobbymatic.com/&quot;>;面向游说者的人工智能自动化平台&lt;/a>;”的公司。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;Yy5Fi2&quot;>;LobbyMatic 在其网站上声称，其人工智能驱动的软件可以做所有事情，例如自动监控国会听证会或“加强研究”立法和监管问题。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;RlJ2CP&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{ “故事”：[{“标题”：“保守党活动家雅各布·沃尔被指控实施选举机器人电话计划”，“url”：“https://www.theverge.com/2020/10/1/21497823/jacob-wohl- jack-burkman-michigan-robocall-voter-intimidation-felony-charges&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;保守派恶作剧者因机器人电话将面临 500 万美元的罚款&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/ 2021/8/24/22640239/fcc-jacob-wohl-burkman-election-robocalls-fine&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Jacob Wohl 的《Predator DC》剧组成员报告拍摄期间遭到袭击&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https: //www.theverge.com/2022/7/22/23273280/jacob-wohl-jack-burkman-predator-dc-film-shoot-assault-allegations- payment&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside >;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;rmIC0H&quot;>;加入人工智能炒作是一项非常值得尊敬的职业举措。问题是，消息人士告诉 Politico，沃尔和伯克曼以“Jay Klein”和“Bill Sanders”的笔名经营该公司。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;x75LuB&quot;>;LobbyMatic其官方网站上没有列出领导层。一家名为...的公司&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/2/24234231/jacob-wohl-jack-burkman-ai-lobbying -lobbymatic-politico&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/2/24234231/jacob-wohl-jack-burkman-ai-lobbying-lobbymatic-politico" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/2/24234231/jacob-wohl-jack-burkman-ai-lobbying-lobbymatic-politico</id><author><name>莎拉·郑</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-02T11:53:10-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-02T11:53:10-04:00</updated><title>绿洲票务混乱促使对动态定价进行调查</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;舞台上的绿洲&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/gCV2bQSj6RG6RGHIAXE304TCE-8=/4x0:4252x2832/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/ chorus_image/image/73558943/2169845513.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;这次巡演标志着 Oasis 自 2009 年 Liam（左）和 Noel Gallagher 解散后乐队的首次重聚。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Gie Knaeps/Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;ojGfp8&quot;>;在 Oasis 歌迷因乐队惊喜重聚巡演被定价后，英国政府承诺调查票务网站使用动态定价的情况。 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/articles/c20r26p7d0ro&quot;>;英国广告监管机构告诉 &lt;em>;BBC 新闻&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;，它已收到 450 起有关误导性机票的投诉价格和可用性，许多门票的价格增加了一倍以上。销售于周六开始，数千名满怀希望的买家在网上排队一整天，几小时内就被抢购一空。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;VbhXYf&quot;>;在 Ticketmaster 上，部分门票的价格从 135 英镑（约合 177 美元）上涨当销售开始时，价格超过 350 英镑（约 460 美元）。英国文化大臣&lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.itv.com%2Fnews%2F2024-08-31%2Foasis- Concert-tickets-2025-general-sale&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F9%2F2%2F24234149%2Foasis-reunion-tour-tickets-dynamic-pricing- probe-uk&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;丽莎·南迪 (Lisa Nandy) 告诉&lt;em>;ITV News&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;，政府将“纳入有关动态定价的透明度和使用的问题，包括...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/2/24234149/oasis-reunion-tour-tickets-dynamic-pricing-probe-uk&quot; >;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/2/24234149/oasis-reunion-tour-tickets-dynamic-pricing-probe-uk" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/2/24234149/oasis-reunion-tour-tickets-dynamic-pricing-probe-uk</id><author><name>杰西韦瑟贝德</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-02T10:43:55-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-02T10:43:55-04:00</updated><title>最佳劳动节销售正在进行中</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;蓝色 Sonos Roam 2 扬声器的营销图片。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/h_OV5PsHkvHflshpa1RuAH38bac=/0x6:2040x1366/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73549916/SonosRoam2_1.16.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Sonos Roam 2 是该公司最新的便携式智能扬声器，已在亚马逊和其他零售商处以近 40 美元的折扣出售。&lt;/em>; |图片：Sonos&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;ItDaxO&quot;>;夏天即将结束时总是令人悲伤。然而，从好的方面来说，劳动节代表着又一个长周末——更不用说在假日购物季真正开始之前有机会节省大量商品。尽管许多劳动节促销早在上周就开始了，但我们仍然看到一系列科技产品的大幅折扣，其中一些折扣可与我们在 7 月份看到的 Prime Day 促销相媲美。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c- float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;0nMQSn&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot; The Verge 2024 年返校礼物指南&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24186140/back-to-school-student-gifts-college-high-school-dorm-accessories-ideas -2024&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Roborock 宠物专用 Q5 Pro 扫地机器人售价不到 200 美元&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/31/24232408/ roborock-q5-pro-robot-vacuum-mop-fellow-stagg-electric-kettle-deal-sale&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Paramount Plus 计划在 2024 年 NFL 赛季之前有 50% 的折扣&quot;,&quot;url&quot; :&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/21/24224474/paramount-plus-with-showtime-subscription-sonos-roam-2-speaker-deal-sale&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div >;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;rvye0m&quot;>;现在，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/dp/B09G9FPHY6?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel= &quot;supported nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Apple 最新一代 iPad&lt;/a>; 促销价不到 200 美元。其他 Verge 批准的商品也跌至历史最低点（或接近历史最低点），包括 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0BW34LCB8/?tag =theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Sonos&#39; Era 100 扬声器&lt;/a>;，亚马逊最新的 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/All-new-Amazon -Echo-Spot-2024-release-Smart-alarm-clock-with-vibrant-sound-Alexa-Black/dp/B0BFC7WQ6R?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Echo Spot &lt;/a>;，以及 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Kindle-Kids-2022-release-worry-free/dp/B0BLJ6LJBM?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener “ target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;入门级 Kindle&lt;/a>;。诚然，我们过去看到许多此类产品的价格略低——而且......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24229577/best-labor -day-sales-2024-tech-deals-laptops-tvs-earbuds&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24229577/best-labor-day-sales-2024-tech-deals-laptops-tvs-earbuds" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24229577/best-labor-day-sales-2024-tech-deals-laptops-tvs-earbuds</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name><name>布兰登·威德</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-02T10:40:33-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-02T10:40:33-04:00</updated><title> Windows 11 现在是最流行的 PC 游戏操作系统</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/9YBYAI9HVz14BdSKZs1UKmwSLys=/0x96:2276x1613/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73558815 /Surface_Laptop_Studio____Gaming.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;lQMIRo&quot;>;微软 Windows 11 操作系统自 2021 年推出以来，Steam 用户使用率首次超过 Windows 10。Windows 10 一直保持强劲势头近年来，尽管微软计划于 2025 年 10 月终止对 Windows 10 的支持。现在有迹象表明，Windows 11 的采用终于朝着微软的正确方向发展。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;yFNJJo&quot;>;Steam 硬件 &lt; a href=&quot;https://store.steampowered.com/hwsurvey/Steam-Hardware-Software-Survey-Welcome-to-Steam&quot;>;8 月份的调查数据&lt;/a>;显示 Windows 11 使用率为 49%，增长了比此前7月份的近46%的数字增长了3个多百分点。 Windows 10 使用率下降了约 3% 至 47%，而 macOS 和 Linux Steam 使用率在 8 月份基本保持不变。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;LnCnSm&quot;>;Windows 11 在网络上的使用率也在增长过去的一年也是如此。在...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/2/24234091/microsoft-windows-11-popular-steam-pc-gaming-survey&quot; >;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/2/24234091/microsoft-windows-11-popular-steam-pc-gaming-survey" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/2/24234091/microsoft-windows-11-popular-steam-pc-gaming-survey</id><author><name>汤姆·沃伦</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-02T10:00:31-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-02T10:00:31-04:00</updated><title>网球是未来的运动吗？</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;矢量插图网球比赛，有一大群人，前景有一台摄像机。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/SriGapI5H-OOBlTELWKZnZV7M4U=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73558752/WHATS_IN_WHATS_OUT_TENNIS_CHORUS_LEDE.0 .jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Samar Haddad for The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;DBBNCW&quot;>;有人向我保证网球的未来在沙漠中。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id= &quot;LrN7hh&quot;>;在沙特阿拉伯吉达举行的下一代 ATP 总决赛的看台上，我看到八号种子阿卜杜拉·谢尔巴赫 (Abdullah Shelbayh) 获得了最戏剧性的出场机会。阿卜杜拉国王体育城的一个体育场内有一片占地近 400 万平方米的足球场和室内竞技场，播音员首先用阿拉伯语然后用英语列出了球员的成就的简短列表。音乐声响起。明亮的白色激光照亮了球场的线条，然后体育场另一端的屏幕打开，露出了一条球员通道，谢尔巴赫从通道中出现，当聚光灯在他周围旋转和……的音量时，他看起来很尴尬和困惑。 p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/c/24225103/tennis-ai-electronic-line-calling-hawk-eye-sports-betting-gambling&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/一个>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/c/24225103/tennis-ai-electronic-line-calling-hawk-eye-sports-betting-gambling" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/c/24225103/tennis-ai-electronic-line-calling-hawk-eye-sports-betting-gambling</id><author><name>凯文·阮</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-02T09:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-02T09:00:00-04:00</updated><title>谷歌 Pixel 9 评测：Android 需要的手机</title><content type="html">&lt;p>;Pixel 9 是一款 Android 旗舰手机，适合那些只想要一部手机的人。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24232480/google-pixel-9-review -屏幕相机电池&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24232480/google-pixel-9-review-screen-camera-battery" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24232480/google-pixel-9-review-screen-camera-battery</id><author><name>艾莉森·约翰逊</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-02T08:43:14-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-02T08:43:14-04:00</updated><title>法官表示，不能强迫社交网络为儿童过滤内容</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;鼠标光标在青少年身上留下阴影的照片拼贴。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/JI39VZmvJdXxNKvPv7VWLPQfvfE=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73558586/STK461_INTERNET_CHILD_SAFETY_Stock_A_ CVirginia.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;UB2MVy&quot;>;一位联邦法官在最后一刻对德克萨斯州的一项法律做出了部分阻止，该法律要求一些大型网络服务来识别未成年人并过滤哪些内容他们在网上看到。该法案名为 HB 18 或《通过家长赋权保护儿童在线安全法案》(SCOPE)，于去年签署成为法律，并将于 9 月 1 日周末生效。但&lt;a href=&quot;https://ecf.txwd.uscourts.gov/doc1/181032749818?caseid=1172798016&quot;>;周五晚法院裁决&lt;/a>;确定“监控和过滤”要求对在线演讲。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;9tfOnN&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://capitol.texas.gov/BillLookup/History.aspx?LegSess=88R&amp;amp;Bill=HB18&quot;>;范围法案&lt;/ a>; 要求一系列网络服务，特别是大型社交网络，对注册年龄低于 18 岁的用户应用特殊规则。这包括限制数据收集、禁止定向广告以及不允许未经...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/2/24232366/texas-scope-act-hb18-blocked-kids-online-safety&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/2/24232366/texas-scope-act-hb18-blocked-kids-online-safety" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/2/24232366/texas-scope-act-hb18-blocked-kids-online-safety</id><author><name>阿迪·罗伯逊</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-02T08:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-02T08:00:00-04:00</updated><title> 160 年前的煤炭理论对自动驾驶的未来有何预测</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;蓝色背景上交替的蓝色和白色车辆的插图&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/tWWoLz4xgL6QQ9EAS-cb2xfYCWQ=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn .vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73558503/acastro_220216_STK003_0004.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;由 Alex Castro / The Verge 绘制的插图&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;f9PhsI&quot;>;之后&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.fastcompany.com/90994141/why-2023-was-the-year-of-the-e-bike-and-not-the-self-driven-car&quot;>;残酷2023 年，自动驾驶汽车的氛围正在改善。 Cruise，行业领导者，其车辆卷入了&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.washingtonpost.com/technology/2023/11/08/cruise-crash-driverless-recall/&quot;>;一场可怕的旧金山车祸&lt;/ a>; 去年秋天，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.cnbc.com/2024/04/09/gms-cruise-to-relaunch-vehicles-with- human-drivers-in-phoenix.html&quot;>;在新管理层的领导下重新启动&lt;/a>;，而竞争对手 Waymo 则&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/waymo-expand-autonomous-ride-hailing-service-areas-los- angeles-san-francisco-2024-08-06/&quot;>;扩张&lt;/a>;以服务湾区和洛杉矶更广泛的地区，特斯拉&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.businessinsider.com/tesla- elon-musk-prioritize-robotaxis-over-cheaper-vehicle-2024-4&quot;>;承诺&lt;/a>;一项新的机器人出租车服务。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;B7j6mL&quot;>;尽管美国人说他们&lt;a href=&quot; https://www.thedrive.com/news/tech/americans-dont-trust-self-driven-cars-want-improved-drivers-ed-instead-study&quot;>;对自动驾驶、助推器保持警惕&lt;/a>;坚持没有什么可害怕的。事实上，他们预计道路上布满自动驾驶汽车的道路将比现状更安全、更清洁，这对于一个交通发达的国家来说是一个诱人的前景&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.epa.gov/ghgemissions/ sources-greenhouse-gas-emissions#:~:text=交通%20部门%20Emissions%20Trends&amp;amp;text=当%20考虑%20only%20direct%20排放时，比%201%25减少%20by%20less%20。&quot;>;温室气体排放&lt;/a>;和居民&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2022-11-03/why-us-traffic-safety-fell-so-far-behind -other-countries&quot;>;死于车祸的可能性比其他国家的人高几倍&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024 /9/2/24232386/self-driven-car-jevons-paradox-robotaxi-waymo-cruise&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/2/24232386/self-driving-car-jevons-paradox-robotaxi-waymo-cruise" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/2/24232386/self-driven-car-jevons-paradox-robotaxi-waymo-cruise</id><author><name>大卫·拉链</name></author></entry></feed>